title: For Trade:  Barebone AR-15's for $2000...give me a break
postcontent:
Those new to Armslist looking for an AR-15 before the high cap ban takes effect basically neutering the rifle please don't get scammed by sellers trying to offload their brand new ARs for double the price.  

Go to www.slickguns.com and you'll see plenty of AR's (reputable builders) in stock at various online stores.  You can even get lowers for $99 shipped plus all the other parts you need to build a good AR for under $1000.  Stock is coming back in and prices are a bit higher, but not double.  

In addition, I'm a little surprised by all the BRAND NEW NEVER FIRED AR's listed for sale here.  I can understand if you bought it and then had something come up where you needed the money, but it seems to be many of the ones listed were bought in order to resale for a profit.  I think one seller has about 10-15 Bushmaster's for sale and he's not a dealer.  Hmmmmm.

There are some great custom AR builds listed on here for good prices, so not everyone is trying to screw the buyers.  Do your research before you jump on what seems to be a good deal only to find out later the seller bought the AR a few weeks ago for half what you paid him/her for it.  

Good luck to all.  I'm sure this will be flagged and removed, but I had to post it anyway.
